Everyone in Socialism would be at like 2<br>
<br>
While in Capitalism would vary widely with an average of about 5-6.<br>
<br>
Thus, the average person would be much better off than the average person in Socialism.  <br>
<br>
I'm not saying Capitalism is perfect, hell, there is no perfect system in my opinion, however, Capitalism is the best system because it, compared to the other system, Socialism, is less flawed and accomodates the fallacys of People rather than correct them.<br>
